      <title>中国央行警告不要“片面”追求信贷扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cbank-warns-against-one-sided-pursuit-credit-expansion-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示银行贷款放缓后，中国央行周四警告称，不要“片面”追求信贷扩张，誓言将优先考虑信贷质量而非规模，并采取措施振兴现有贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cbank-warns-against-one-sided-pursuit-credit-expansion-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:44:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达能超出第一季度销售预期，保持 2024 年目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-q1-sales-beat-forecasts-keeps-2024-goals-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达能周四公布的季度销售额强于预期，所有业务均实现销量增长，因为这家全球最大的酸奶制造商设法提高价格以应对更高的投入成本，尽管速度比之前慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-q1-sales-beat-forecasts-keeps-2024-goals-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国官方媒体称，日本在寻求更紧密关系的同时警告中国威胁是“两面派”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-two-faced-seeking-closer-ties-while-warning-china-threat-chinese-state-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国官方报纸周四发表社论，谴责“双面”日本在追求更稳定的双边关系的同时，错误地将其描述为地区安全威胁，并警告称，如果东京鲁莽行事，中国将采取措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-two-faced-seeking-closer-ties-while-warning-china-threat-chinese-state-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迅达重申2024年销售目标，但警告中国市场疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-posts-q1-order-intake-slightly-above-expectations-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电梯和自动扶梯制造商迅达周四重申了全年收入指引，即低个位数百分比增长，尽管该公司在充满挑战的经济背景下下调了对中国新安装电梯的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-posts-q1-order-intake-slightly-above-expectations-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 04:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
